@startuml
title 两点标定流程 - 时序图

actor "操作者" as User
participant "CalibrationDialog" as Dialog
participant "ImageViewport" as Viewport
participant "CalibrationService" as Service
participant "ObservationSession" as Session

User -> Dialog: 选择标定工具
Dialog -> Viewport: request pick two image points
User -> Viewport: 点击标尺第一端
User -> Viewport: 点击标尺第二端
Viewport --> Dialog: imagePointA, imagePointB
User -> Dialog: 输入真实长度和单位
Dialog -> Service: createProfile(points, length, unit)
Service --> Dialog: CalibrationProfile
Dialog -> Session: setCalibration(profile)
Session -> Session: recalculateMeasurements()

@enduml

